020: Subfield a may have invalid characters.
020: Subfield a may have invalid characters.
020: Subfield a has bad checksum, 1-54879-474-5 (hyphens and bad checksum).
020: Subfield a qualifier must be preceded by space, 1548794740(10 : unspaced qualifier).
